OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782748079
OL,3,CBody found in search for boy missing
OL,4,Cin river
OL,6,FThe body of a teenage boy has been
OL,7,Frecovered from the water after reports
OL,8,Fhe got into difficulty.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FRiver Irwell at Clifton Country Park
OL,12,Fin Swinton, Salford, shortly after
OL,13,F4.50pm on Saturday, 27 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
