OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782748079
OL,3,CBody found in search for boy missing
OL,4,Cin river
OL,6,FSpecialist teams from Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police (GMP), Greater
OL,8,FManchester Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,F(GMFRS) and North West Ambulance
OL,10,FService (NWAS) spent 36 hours
OL,11,Fsearching the area before a body was
OL,12,Flocated by the North West Under Water
OL,13,FSearch and Marine Unit.
OL,15,FFormal identification has yet to take
OL,16,Fplace, but specialist officers are
OL,17,Fsupporting the family of the 15-year-
OL,18,Fold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
