CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782748079
OL,3,CBody found in search for boy missing
OL,4,Cin river
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Dave Ogden from
OL,7,FSalford CID said: "Saturday's incident
OL,8,Fis truly heart breaking, and my
OL,9,Fthoughts remain with the family and
OL,10,Floved ones of the young boy who has so
OL,11,Ftragically lost his life.
OL,13,F"While we are satisfied there are no
OL,14,Fsuspicious circumstances, this
OL,15,Fincident is an incredibly upsetting
OL,16,Freminder of the serious risks
OL,17,Fassociated with open water.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
