OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782748079
OL,3,CBody found in search for boy missing
OL,4,Cin river
OL,6,F"We understand people want to make the
OL,7,Fmost of the warm weather, but we would
OL,8,Furge everyone to stay safe and avoid
OL,9,Fentering reservoirs, rivers, canals or
OL,10,Fponds.
OL,12,F"Please take care and enjoy the
OL,13,Fweather in a safe way."
OL,15,FThe news brings the total number of
OL,16,Fdrownings across the country during
OL,17,Fthe recent heatwave to eight.
OL,19,FThe boy has not been named and no
OL,20,Ffurther information has been given.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@WO]
